data.description: Nestled in a serene and peaceful locale, this remarkable property at 200 Capitol Avenue in Winder, Georgia offers the perfect blend of tranquility and convenience. Situated in a quiet area, this home boasts a spacious lot, providing a sense of privacy and room to breathe. One of the standout features of this property is its strategic location, with easy access to both the 2-11 and 85 highways, making commuting a breeze. Furthermore, its close proximity to a diverse array of restaurants and its convenient distance to downtown make it an ideal residence for those seeking both convenience and a vibrant community atmosphere. This charming home welcomes you with its cozy ambiance, featuring 3 bedrooms that provide ample space for relaxation and comfortable living. The kitchen is a chef's delight, equipped with modern, stainless steel open-concept appliances and well-maintained white cabinets and laminate countertops, seamlessly combining style and functionality. Step outside onto the rear porch, a delightful retreat that invites you to unwind in the afternoons or bask in the warm sunlight. Whether you're sipping your morning coffee or entertaining guests, this outdoor space adds an extra layer of charm to the property. Don't miss the opportunity to call this delightful residence your own, where quiet sophistication meets convenience, and modern comforts blend seamlessly with the tranquility of the surroundings. Welcome to your new home at 200 Capitol Avenue – where living is an art, and every moment is a masterpiece.
